---
title: Cheesy Beef and Mushroom Calzones with Marinara
description: Grab the kids and get them to help with tonight's easy cheesy beef calzones. The DIY garlicky sauce is the ultimate calzone dipper and comes together with just the stir of a spoon. The kids can even mix and match their fillings... it's a win-win dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R1006_W31_CA_RB153160-3_Main_low-25c82cd6.jpg
